Package org.hatemile

The org.hatemile package contains the interfaces with the acessibility solutions.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AccessibleAssociation
    The AccessibleAssociation interface improve accessibility, associating elements.
    AccessibleCSS
    The AccessibleCSS interface improve accessibility of CSS.
    AccessibleDisplay
    The AccessibleDisplay interface improve accessibility, showing informations.
    AccessibleEvent
    The AccessibleEvent interface improve the accessibility, making elements events available from a keyboard.
    AccessibleForm
    The AccessibleForm interface improve the accessibility of forms.
    AccessibleNavigation
    The AccessibleNavigation interface improve the accessibility of navigation.
